flavorText: Even the most skilled of modern mages only partially understand the Conch Horn's awesome powers.
name: Conch Horn
originalText:
o1, oc
T: Sacrifice Conch Horn. Draw two cards, then put any one card from your hand back on top of your library.

rulings.text: You draw two cards, then put one back as part of the same effect. You can’t do anything in between. Anything that triggers off of card drawing will wait until you finish resolving this ability before going on the stack.

text: {1}, {T}, Sacrifice Conch Horn: Draw two cards, then put a card from your hand on top of your library.
